                     <interp inst="t18210606-54-person627" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , we went to the sea side, nothing was done that night, Griffiths was not with us that night.</p>
               <p>Q. Were you applied to, to go at another time - A. I went on my own account. On Easter Monday Underwood had given me information, and I went to 
               <persName id="t18210606-54-person628">
                  John 
                  Richardson
