            , gave me my cartridge, I had twelve, I had a gun which I carried from my home, I saw them all served with fire-arms, except Webster, I did not see him have any, all the prisoners had them except him, they were mostly large pistols, I saw no cartridges served except to myself, 
               <persName id="t18210606-54-person638">
                  John 
                  Richardson
               <interp inst="t18210606-54-person638" type="surname" value="Richardson"></interp>
